content.rendered:
Data Entry | Tulsa, Oklahoma
  • Full-Time, Monday-Friday 8:00am-5:00pm
  • 2 years insurance or medical office experience required
  • High School Diploma or equivalent
  • Experience with EMR a plus
  • Will assist with entry of Medicaid charges, including faxing documentation and secondary claim
  • Will process and coordinate Indian Health claims, referrals, and Purchase orders
  • Will assist with filing, pulling reports and scanning
  • $12+/hour
